name: One week notice
description:
This is a real brainstorm when you work with VR every day!
At some point, images and forms are intertwined with reality, because for our unconscious all these images are real, especially those feelings that arise in the process of creation and perception. Somewhere deep inside, I adapt to this unknown modality every day. I'm changing, I believe for the better.

Artwork created by Maksym Denysenko in 2021 using VR.
